// EdgeContextMenu
// Right-click context menu for edges in the diagram editor.
// Provides: Edit Label, Change Origin, Change Destination, Delete Edge.
// Closes on outside click or Escape.

MenuItem and Divider are small layout primitives used within the menu.

FUNCTION EdgeContextMenu(edgeId, label, position, onEditLabel, onChangeOrigin, onChangeDestination, onDelete, onClose) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Renders a positioned menu at the given screen coordinates.
  Closes on mousedown outside the menu element.
  Closes on Escape key.

---

FUNCTION handleEditLabel() -> void
  Prompts user for a new label. IF not null, calls onEditLabel(newLabel). Closes.

---

FUNCTION handleChangeOrigin() -> void
  Calls onChangeOrigin (parent enters origin-selection mode). Closes.

---

FUNCTION handleChangeDestination() -> void
  Calls onChangeDestination. Closes.

---

FUNCTION handleDelete() -> void
  Confirms with user. IF confirmed, calls onDelete. Closes.
